            {
              "id": "CVE-2026-35360",
              "name": "OsPackageVulnerability",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The touch utility in uutils coreutils is vulnerable to a Time-of-Check ..."
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "The touch utility in uutils coreutils is vulnerable to a Time-of-Check to Time-of-Use (TOCTOU) race condition during file creation. When the utility identifies a missing path, it later attempts creation using File::create(), which internally uses O_TRUNC. An attacker can exploit this window to create a file or swap a symlink at the target path, causing touch to truncate an existing file and leading to permanent data loss."
              },
